comment: Ellis (DAL) steps on Smith's (HOU) foot on the drive and he falls to the ground but the contact is incidental.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Ellis (DAL), but it does not affect his ability to defend.

Smith (HOU) makes body to body contact with Nowitzki (DAL) after he is caught in the air because of the pump fake. Nowitzki was not in a shooting motion at the time of the foul and was awarded 2 FT's because Houston was in the penalty.
Howard (HOU) sets the screen on Ellis (DAL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Chandler (DAL) makes contact with Harden's (HOU) body and it affects his layup attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Nowitzki's (DAL) body as he begins his upward shooting motion on the jump shot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Nowitzki (DAL) was attempting a 3 point field goal when he was fouled by Harden (HOU) was upheld.
Smith (HOU) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Ellis' (DAL) driving layup.
Ellis (DAL) commits a take foul on Brewer (HOU).
Smith (HOU) does not make contact with Nowitzki (DAL) as he tries to knock away the inbounds pass.
